    "causal_summary": "That left a production asymmetry. The index path can write Jina v3 vectors into `vec_1024`, while query-time `generateEmbedding()` and `generateQueryEmbedding()` can still instantiate llama-cpp and produce 768-dim EmbeddingGemma vectors. The live machine has `vec_metadata.active_embedder_name='jina-embeddings-v3'`, `active_embedder_dim=1024`, and a populated `vec_1024`, so search must encode queries with the same Ollama-backed model.",
